Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.87,0:00:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你們幾個把劍拔出來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.52,0:00:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那傢伙出現的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.49,0:00:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}機會只有一瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.44,0:00:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}跑起來!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.57,0:00:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}好快!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.59,0:00:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}在這森林裡根本無法迴避
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.43,0:00:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}要被追上了!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.74,0:00:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}士官長 請求進入立體機動狀態!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.35,0:00:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}士官長!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.73,0:00:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5} 休想得逞!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.62,0:00:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}從後方來了增援!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.79,0:01:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}士官長! 下令啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.83,0:01:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}快點啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.91,0:01:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那傢伙太危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.58,0:01:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我們應該出手了!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.12,0:01:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}再這樣下去會被追上的!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.89,0:01:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我們必須在這裡阻止她!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.36,0:01:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我們是為了這個才進入森林的!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.31,0:01:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是這樣對吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.35,0:01:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}士官長!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.43,0:01:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}士官長 請你下令!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.42,0:01:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5} 所有人把耳朵摀住
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.47,0:03:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}震撼彈?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.54,0:03:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你們的工作是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.62,0:03:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}只會憑藉著情感做事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.03,0:03:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}應該不是這樣對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.28,0:03:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}本班的使命是要保護這個臭小子不能受到一點傷害
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.74,0:03:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}到死為止
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.95,0:03:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不是為了要監視我...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.42,0:03:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我們就這樣繼續騎馬向前進
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.35,0:03:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}聽到沒?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.14,0:03:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}了解!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.50,0:03:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}繼續前進?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.09,0:03:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}到底要前進多遠?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.67,0:04:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}而且那傢伙已經近在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.07,0:04:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.01,0:04:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是增援!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.02,0:04:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我們不快點幫他掩護的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.46,0:04:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}又會被幹掉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.69,0:04:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連 給我向前看!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.74,0:04:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}君達先生...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.11,0:04:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不要亂了腳步
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.57,0:04:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}維持最高速度
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.19,0:04:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾魯多先生...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.88,0:04:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}為什麼!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.10,0:04:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}里維班不出手的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.64,0:04:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}還有誰能夠阻止那傢伙!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.84,0:04:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}又有人犧牲了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.05,0:04:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}明明他或許能夠得救的...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.94,0:04:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}還有一個人在作戰!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.67,0:04:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}現在的話還來得及!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.20,0:04:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連 你給我往前看 繼續跑!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.76,0:04:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}妳是叫我逃避戰鬥嗎!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.45,0:04:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}妳要我眼睜睜看著夥伴被殺嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.34,0:04:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}對 沒錯!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.87,0:04:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}給我遵從士官長的指示
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.95,0:04:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我不懂為什麼要見死不救!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.37,0:04:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你們不說明我也不知道理由啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.76,0:04:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這是為什麼?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.04,0:04:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}因為士官長認為現在不應該說明!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.05,0:05:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你之所以不懂是因為你還是菜鳥!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.15,0:05:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}了解的話就給我閉嘴遵從指示
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.98,0:05:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.56,0:05:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我自己一個人不也能戰鬥嗎...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.46,0:05:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}為什麼我老是去依靠人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.82,0:05:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我自己去戰鬥不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.94,0:05:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你在做什麼艾連!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.60,0:05:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}只有你性命受到威脅時才被允許這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.28,0:05:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我們不是說好了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.53,0:05:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.57,0:05:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你的做法並沒有錯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.70,0:05:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}想做的話就去做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.25,0:05:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}其實我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.06,0:05:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這小子是個真正的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.93,0:05:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}跟「巨人之力」沒有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.43,0:06:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不管用什麼力量去壓制他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.03,0:06:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不管把他關進多深的地牢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.55,0:06:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}也沒有人能夠讓他的意識就此屈服
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.74,0:06:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}總之我想去把巨人給幹掉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.05,0:06:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.45,0:06:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我們之所以會有判斷上的差異
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.96,0:06:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}都是因為經驗的影響
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.44,0:06:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}但是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.72,0:06:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你不必去依靠那有的沒的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.80,0:06:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}選擇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.69,0:06:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}看你是要相信自己
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.05,0:06:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}還是要相信我跟這群人以及調查軍團組織
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.95,0:06:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我也不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.91,0:06:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}一直以來都是這樣...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.77,0:06:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就算相信自己的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.00,0:06:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}相信值得信賴的夥伴的選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.58,0:06:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}也沒有人知道結果到底會如何
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.55,0:06:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}所以...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.96,0:06:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}至少
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.81,0:06:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}選擇一個自己不會留下遺憾的作法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.38,0:07:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.65,0:07:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}相信我們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.40,0:07:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我想到一個可以把你弄到半死的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.62,0:07:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}蛤?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.16,0:07:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}雖然我說要阻止變成巨人的你只能把你給殺了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.54,0:07:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不過用這個方法你頂多重傷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.39,0:07:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}但還是要看每個人的實力技巧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.26,0:07:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}簡單來說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.57,0:07:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就是把後頸上的肉跟你一起切下來就好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.24,0:07:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}到時候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.47,0:07:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}應該會把你的手腳前端給切掉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.38,0:07:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}反正你會像蜥蜴一樣再生不是?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.58,0:07:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}真夠噁心的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.42,0:07:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}請等一下...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.42,0:07:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我不知道要怎樣才能再長出來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.20,0:08:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}有沒有其他方法...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.99,0:08:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}「不想冒任何風險 也不想作任何犧牲」嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.19,0:08:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.43,0:08:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那就給我做好覺悟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.36,0:08:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我們也是一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.35,0:08:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}冒著被你給殺掉的危險
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.92,0:08:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}所以你放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.07,0:08:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.62,0:08:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.85,0:08:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那... 那麼可以進行實驗吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.19,0:08:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}風險太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.11,0:08:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}雖這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.48,0:08:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}但不對這小子好好檢驗一下也不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.67,0:08:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}可以讓我來計畫吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.31,0:08:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.55,0:08:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}如果有不懂的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.34,0:08:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}搞懂了就好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.16,0:08:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這值得我們賭上自己的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.03,0:08:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}去嘗試它
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.74,0:08:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}差不多可以了吧? 艾連
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.29,0:08:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}準備好之後會用信號彈通知你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.85,0:08:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}接下來交給你自行判斷了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.94,0:08:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}了解
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.76,0:09:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}如果是這個枯井
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.32,0:09:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}應該能夠困住喪失自我意識的巨人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.01,0:09:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}才對...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.70,0:09:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}信號來了...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.35,0:09:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}上次操作巨人是為了封住牆壁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.01,0:09:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}如果又失控
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.28,0:09:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這次可能會被里維班給殺了也說不定
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.39,0:09:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}他沒注意到信號彈嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.22,0:09:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.95,0:09:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是他變成巨人的條件不是很明確才對
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.00,0:09:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}喂 艾連!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.71,0:09:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}先暫停吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.20,0:09:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}發生了什麼嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.96,0:09:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}漢吉分隊長...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.82,0:09:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我無法變成巨人...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.24,0:10:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}連自己咬的手也不會復原嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.55,0:10:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.22,0:10:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}如果你沒有辦法變成巨人的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.99,0:10:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}要封住瑪利亞之牆就成了無稽之談了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.90,0:10:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這是命令
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.56,0:10:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}給我想好辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.82,0:10:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}好...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.37,0:10:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不要太氣餒啊 艾連
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.79,0:10:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.87,0:10:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}唉 就只是你比想像中接近人類而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.78,0:10:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}比起心急送命好多了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.41,0:10:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你的嘗試也不是沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.20,0:10:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.38,0:10:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這種事還是謹慎點好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.41,0:10:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}為什麼大家這麼的冷靜...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.18,0:10:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}難道我沒變成巨人也沒差嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.70,0:11:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你還好嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.74,0:11:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.23,0:11:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}喂...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.13,0:11:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}啥鬼?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.99,0:11:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這爆炸是...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.06,0:11:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}為什麼現在才...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.69,0:11:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}冷靜點...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.20,0:11:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}里維士官長...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.89,0:11:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這是...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.93,0:11:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我就說了冷靜一點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.09,0:11:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你們幾個...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.58,0:12:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.47,0:12:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}什麼聲音?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.04,0:12:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.33,0:12:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這是怎麼回事!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.55,0:12:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}蛤?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.67,0:12:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}為什麼你剛才未經許可就變身?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.53,0:12:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}給我回答!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.34,0:12:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾爾多 你等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.13,0:12:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}給我回答艾連
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.45,0:12:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你打算做什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.61,0:12:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.54,0:12:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那個等下再說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.36,0:12:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}請你證明...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.83,0:12:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你對我們... 對人類並沒有敵意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.94,0:12:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}證明啊! 快點!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.75,0:12:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你有這個責任
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.47,0:12:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你有種給我動那隻手看看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.03,0:13:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}動的那一瞬間你腦袋就會搬家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.49,0:13:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我可真的做的到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.26,0:13:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你要不要試試看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.36,0:13:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}歐魯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.25,0:13:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我叫你冷靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.40,0:13:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}士官長
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.33,0:13:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}請你離艾連遠一點!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.80,0:13:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你太接近了!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.71,0:13:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不 該離遠點的是你們
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.49,0:13:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}給我退後
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.98,0:13:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}為什麼!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.85,0:13:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}因為我的直覺
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.74,0:13:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}怎麼啦! 艾連
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.79,0:13:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你倒是說說話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.02,0:13:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.55,0:13:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}休想輕舉妄動!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.57,0:13:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你快點證明啊!! 艾連
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.32,0:13:21.25,Upside,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就說了...我自己也...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.00,0:13:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}回答啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.81,0:13:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你以為我們不會殺你嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.95,0:13:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我可是認真的 快點啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.89,0:13:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你聽不懂嗎!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.06,0:13:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}要幹掉你囉!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.10,0:13:28.66,Upside,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我對人類...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.44,0:13:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你們給我稍微閉嘴一下!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.57,0:13:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連~!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.17,0:13:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我可以摸摸你的手嗎??
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.67,0:13:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}喂 可以吧? 沒問題對吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.23,0:13:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我只是摸一下而已!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.70,0:13:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}漢吉分隊長...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.82,0:13:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}請等等...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.31,0:13:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}好...好燙喔!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.80,0:13:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}沒有皮膚感覺超燙的啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.78,0:13:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這東西燙到爆!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.79,0:14:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}分隊長 你太激動了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.20,0:14:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}喂 艾連你不會覺得燙嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.76,0:14:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}跟你右手相連的部位怎樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.61,0:14:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我超想看的!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.57,0:14:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}對了!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.75,0:14:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}只要快點把這隻手給拔出來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.29,0:14:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}可惡的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.70,0:14:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}喂! 艾連
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.90,0:14:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你可別亂來!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.97,0:14:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}欸!! 艾連 你太快了啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.73,0:14:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我還有想調查的...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.83,0:14:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}士官長...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.53,0:14:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}現在感覺如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.07,0:14:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}感覺...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.16,0:14:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不是...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.16,0:14:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}很好...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.39,0:15:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我不知道他們真的會對我充滿敵意...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.76,0:15:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}自己竟然那麼不被信任...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.35,0:15:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這當然
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.10,0:15:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就是因為他們是這樣才選了他們
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.06,0:15:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}雖然調查軍團的原則是「能夠活著回來才算獨當一面」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.01,0:15:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}跟巨人對峙時 我們的情報總是不足
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.95,0:15:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不管你怎麼思考無法理解的狀況還是太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.25,0:15:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那麼你該做的就是迅速的行動
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.19,0:15:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}以及事先設想最壞打算作出異於常人的決定
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.01,0:15:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}話是這樣說 但我們也不是沒血沒淚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.28,0:15:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}當他們拿武器指著你時也不是完全無感的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.87,0:15:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}里維士官長
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.25,0:15:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}漢吉分隊長找你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.48,0:16:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}拉屎也太久了吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.34,0:16:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}才沒有呢 順暢得很呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.93,0:16:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}因為跟上層的人說明花了點時間
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.32,0:16:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}總之你們先看看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.13,0:16:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}妳說這支茶匙嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.61,0:16:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.25,0:16:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}從艾連身上長出的巨人右手就抓著它
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.91,0:16:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}像這樣用拇指跟食指握著
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.91,0:16:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}欸?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.01,0:16:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}很難想像是偶然握住的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.81,0:16:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}而且看起來也沒有遇熱或因壓力而變形呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.50,0:16:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你有想到什麼嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.72,0:16:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}記得當時我想要去撿它
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.47,0:16:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}然後就變成巨人了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.73,0:16:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}原來如此...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.84,0:16:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這次你無法變成巨人或許就是這個原因
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.59,0:16:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}「殺死巨人」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.33,0:16:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}「抵擋砲彈」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.96,0:16:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}「扛起巨岩」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.24,0:17:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}每次的狀況都是在變成巨人之前有著明確的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.09,0:17:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我想光靠自殘行為無法成為啟動的關鍵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.89,0:17:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}必須要有某種目的才行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.07,0:17:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這次變成巨人確實跟抵擋砲彈時的狀況有些類似
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.46,0:17:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.09,0:17:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}為了「撿湯匙」而變成巨人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.63,0:17:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這是怎麼回事...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.33,0:17:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}所以你並不是刻意要去違背約定的囉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.65,0:17:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.85,0:17:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}等一下...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.82,0:17:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你們在幹嘛啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.56,0:17:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}好痛...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.90,0:17:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這還真痛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.98,0:18:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連沒想到你真的咬下去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.03,0:18:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我們判斷錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.82,0:18:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這只是一點代價而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.14,0:18:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}雖然這麼做根本算不了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.78,0:18:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}負責壓制你是我們的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.82,0:18:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這件事情本身並沒有錯!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.35,0:18:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你別得意忘形了啊 小鬼!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.66,0:18:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}對不起 艾連...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.89,0:18:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}當時我們嚇得半死又愚蠢地
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.59,0:18:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}想必讓你很失望吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.30,0:18:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不過...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.55,0:18:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就算這樣...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.05,0:18:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我們還是很需要你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.37,0:18:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}希望你也能依賴我們
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.47,0:18:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}所以...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.58,0:18:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}請你...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.19,0:18:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}相信我們...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.50,0:18:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.81,0:18:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}太慢了!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.41,0:18:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}給我趕快決定!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.61,0:19:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}前進!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.07,0:19:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}放開我!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.66,0:19:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}對不起!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.51,0:19:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}目標加速了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.84,0:19:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}衝啊!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.90,0:19:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就這樣逃離她!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.57,0:19:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.03,0:19:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}怎麼逃得掉...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.00,0:19:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}如果再這樣背對著她跑的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.37,0:19:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那些人都會被踩扁的...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.23,0:19:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}雖然...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.66,0:19:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}命在旦夕...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.87,0:19:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}眼睜睜看著同伴送死...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.13,0:19:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}大家依然選擇繼續前進
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.26,0:19:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}里維士官長也始終盯著前方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.46,0:19:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}而學長姐們...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.29,0:20:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}也都信任士官長 將一切託付給他...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.74,0:20:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我也想去相信他們
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.08,0:20:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就像他們相信我一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.31,0:20:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}發射!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.67,0:20:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}再往前一點之後就把馬繫好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.23,0:20:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}然後進入立體機動
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.31,0:20:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我要暫時獨自行動
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.57,0:21:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}接下來給艾爾多指揮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.86,0:21:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}與那巨人保持適當距離後把艾連藏起來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.03,0:21:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}馬就交給你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.62,0:21:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.63,0:21:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你們打算...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.54,0:21:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}活捉那個巨人?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.75,0:21:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}怎麼樣啊 艾連?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.84,0:21:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}看到沒!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.77,0:21:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我們已經抓到那個巨人了!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.21,0:21:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這就是調查軍團的實力!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.33,0:21:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你這笨蛋可別小看我們啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.23,0:21:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}怎樣啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.90,0:21:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這下懂了吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.79,0:21:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.16,0:21:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}她應該已經動不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.90,0:21:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}還不能大意
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.99,0:21:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不過你們竟然有辦法把她引到這裡來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.85,0:21:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}多虧後面的班跟她拚命才爭取到一些時間
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.71,0:21:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}如果沒有他們就不可能成功
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.46,0:21:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這樣啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.91,0:21:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.83,0:22:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}多虧了他們...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.74,0:22:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}才有機會見到躲在這傢伙後頸裡的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.21,0:22:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}希望那傢伙不要在這裡面挫到尿出來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.91,0:23:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾爾文．史密斯的機密作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.96,0:23:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}此作戰是以捕獲女巨人為目的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.97,0:24:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}調查軍團表示要揭穿她的真實身分
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.88,0:24:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.86,0:12:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}
